The '''Sebiris Run''' was a hyperspace route located in the [[Kathol sector/Legends|Kathol sector]] in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]] of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. This hyperlane along with the [[Galtea Run]] originated at [[Pembric II]] at the terminus of the [[Trition Trade Route]]. These two hyperroutes were the only spacelanes that crossed the [[Marcol Void/Legends|Marcol Void]]. The Sebiris Run connected [[Sebiris]] with the worlds of the [[Pimbrellan League]], such as [[Dolstan]] and [[Swedlan]], before intersecting with the Galatea Run at [[Timbra Ott]].<ref name="TKO">''[[The Kathol Outback]]''</ref>

